{"tid":829264,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩, 屌你老母, 真係唔好買STRONTIUM既產品","createTime":"2018-09-20T10:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T22:14:25.000Z","uid":153662,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6895cdc17843d17c38b80f4f89e9e3f556394d52","tid":829264,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/175604_467d1817efff55ba077837b528ec784c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F175604_467d1817efff55ba077837b528ec784c.jpg&h=127e59fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我想買呢隻OTG TYPE C好耐, 見佢寫UP TO 150MB READ 同100MB WRITE, 返黎咪試下佢<br />\n<br />\n用左兩部機去試, 出左咁既RESULT比我, 眼都凸埋<br />\nSPEC:<br />\n6700HQ/ 16GB DDR4 2400/ USB-C THUNDERBOLT PORT<br />\n4790/ 16GB DDR3 2400/ USB-A 3.0<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/180435_8174dd350775711122648670870e7422.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F180435_8174dd350775711122648670870e7422.PNG&h=00cb6e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/180443_8eb8c00c550586c82a332e82e8e5059f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F180443_8eb8c00c550586c82a332e82e8e5059f.PNG&h=ec83ad2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日打去代理問係咪隻手指唔正常,<span style=\"color: red;\"> 最撚嬲條聽電話既8婆用西聲答我:「UP TO JA MA, 唔會去到架WO」</span><br />\n<br />\n我當堂呆撚左, 我答佢, 我知唔會到, 但唔會差咁遠呀嘛, 差成1/3 WO<br />\n另一隻牌字既都唔會咁誇張<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8婆西聲話:「咁你覺得有問題咪拎黎CHECK囉」</span><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n附上另一隻<span style=\"color: orange;\">VERBATIM既測試, 人地標110MB READ/ 20MB WRITE</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/180627_172c0bbce48c41f51e900d30f3542b13.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F180627_172c0bbce48c41f51e900d30f3542b13.PNG&h=4e4ff7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/180632_58491cb3c72b0d56b47e71d5cfe9587d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F180632_58491cb3c72b0d56b47e71d5cfe9587d.PNG&h=dfa4c5ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3fb6b4e0a875179974527852bbe22f843a0b775","tid":829264,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"屌, 做唔慣惡人, 唔柒識當面爆9佢"},{"pid":"6ad2d20fa2f7b8fe163e333de3abdd5ea03b1abf","tid":829264,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3fb6b4e0a875179974527852bbe22f843a0b775","tid":829264,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"屌, 做唔慣惡人, 唔柒識當面爆9佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"當你買多幾隻就知佢算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334062fa210f74b3ee76669358a37ee10f63de59","tid":829264,"uid":42879,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6ad2d20fa2f7b8fe163e333de3abdd5ea03b1abf","tid":829264,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3fb6b4e0a875179974527852bbe22f843a0b775","tid":829264,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"屌, 做唔慣惡人, 唔柒識當面爆9佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"當你買多幾隻就知佢算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"食多幾次屎就知垃圾好食？"},{"pid":"312ac1334576adcfab04dd1f4d58ec0ccf50a372","tid":829264,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ad2d20fa2f7b8fe163e333de3abdd5ea03b1abf","tid":829264,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3fb6b4e0a875179974527852bbe22f843a0b775","tid":829264,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislik